title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week 1
description:
The whole crew is back and fired up for the first full slate of the year. Week Zero wasn't great as Dave was the only one who came out over .500. Dave and Big Cat have HUGE cards and need their junkyard dog Rico back.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
